title: Vaults of Terra - (Space Marine) Chapters - Iron Hands
description:
The Vaults of Terra introduce the final video before the start of the Imperial guard Series, the Iron Hands Space Marine chapter, whose will is as hard as the metal for which they're named.

The Imperial Guard will be starting next video, so vote for what you want to see when we start talking about the Hammer of the Emperor, along with your votes for chapters in the on-going chapter's series. 

Vaults of Terra Intro:
Stealth Shock

Intro Music: 
Daniel Yount - Dark Times
